=== Why I wrote this page ===

I’ve always felt like Deadzone levels portray danger too quickly, obliterating the wanderer before they are able to say “Candidate for Deletion”. This level is meant to convey that Deadzones and other dangerous levels do not have to be fast-paced, but can instead slaughter the wanderer in unique, underutilized ways.
